---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import LessonNav from '../../components/LessonNav.astro';
import LessonAudio from '../../components/LessonAudio.astro';
---
<Layout title="Lesson 7: Robot Subsystems & Technical Pages">
  <div class="lesson-header">
    <span class="lesson-badge">Lesson 7</span>
    <h1>Robot Subsystems & Technical Pages</h1>
    <p class="lesson-subtitle">How to document each part of your robot clearly and effectively.</p>
    <LessonAudio slug="lesson-6" />
  </div>

  <p>
    This lesson is all about documenting your robot's individual subsystems and technical components in a way that makes sense to judges.
  </p>

  <h2>What Are Subsystems?</h2>
  <p>
    Subsystems are basically the individual mechanical, electrical, and software parts that make up your robot.
    Each one serves a specific purpose and plays into your robot's overall performance.
  </p>

  <h2>Typical Subsystems</h2>

  <div class="subsystem-grid">
    <div class="sub-card">
      <div class="sub-icon">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/><path d="M19.4 15a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 .33 1.82l.06.06a2 2 0 0 1-2.83 2.83l-.06-.06a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.82-.33 1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1 1.51V21a2 2 0 0 1-4 0v-.09A1.65 1.65 0 0 0 9 19.4a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.82.33l-.06.06a2 2 0 0 1-2.83-2.83l.06-.06A1.65 1.65 0 0 0 4.68 15a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.51-1H3a2 2 0 0 1 0-4h.09A1.65 1.65 0 0 0 4.6 9a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-.33-1.82l-.06-.06a2 2 0 0 1 2.83-2.83l.06.06A1.65 1.65 0 0 0 9 4.68a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1-1.51V3a2 2 0 0 1 4 0v.09a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1 1.51 1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1.82-.33l.06-.06a2 2 0 0 1 2.83 2.83l-.06.06A1.65 1.65 0 0 0 19.4 9a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1.51 1H21a2 2 0 0 1 0 4h-.09a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.51 1z"/></svg>
      </div>
      <strong>Drive(train) System</strong>
      <p>How your robot moves: wheels, motors, gearing</p>
    </div>
    <div class="sub-card">
      <div class="sub-icon">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M21 16V8a2 2 0 0 0-1-1.73l-7-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 0l-7 4A2 2 0 0 0 3 8v8a2 2 0 0 0 1 1.73l7 4a2 2 0 0 0 2 0l7-4A2 2 0 0 0 21 16z"/></svg>
      </div>
      <strong>Intake System</strong>
      <p>How your robot collects game elements</p>
    </div>
    <div class="sub-card">
      <div class="sub-icon">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polygon points="13 2 3 14 12 14 11 22 21 10 12 10 13 2"/></svg>
      </div>
      <strong>Scoring Mechanism</strong>
      <p>How your robot scores points</p>
    </div>
    <div class="sub-card">
      <div class="sub-icon">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="23 6 13.5 15.5 8.5 10.5 1 18"/><polyline points="17 6 23 6 23 12"/></svg>
      </div>
      <strong>Hanging / Climbing</strong>
      <p>How your robot hangs or climbs (if applicable)</p>
    </div>
    <div class="sub-card">
      <div class="sub-icon">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect x="4" y="4" width="16" height="16" rx="2" ry="2"/><rect x="9" y="9" width="6" height="6"/><line x1="9" y1="1" x2="9" y2="4"/><line x1="15" y1="1" x2="15" y2="4"/><line x1="9" y1="20" x2="9" y2="23"/><line x1="15" y1="20" x2="15" y2="23"/><line x1="20" y1="9" x2="23" y2="9"/><line x1="20" y1="14" x2="23" y2="14"/><line x1="1" y1="9" x2="4" y2="9"/><line x1="1" y1="14" x2="4" y2="14"/></svg>
      </div>
      <strong>Control System</strong>
      <p>Sensors and electronics that manage everything</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2>How to Document Each Subsystem</h2>
  <p>For each subsystem, include:</p>

  <div class="doc-checklist">
    <div class="check-item">
      <span class="check-icon">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 16v-4"/><path d="M12 8h.01"/></svg>
      </span>
      <div>
        <strong>Purpose</strong>
        <p>What does this subsystem do?</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="check-item">
      <span class="check-icon">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="1 4 1 10 7 10"/><path d="M3.51 15a9 9 0 1 0 2.13-9.36L1 10"/></svg>
      </span>
      <div>
        <strong>Design Evolution</strong>
        <p>How did it improve throughout the season?</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="check-item">
      <span class="check-icon">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect x="2" y="7" width="20" height="14" rx="2" ry="2"/><path d="M16 21V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16"/></svg>
      </span>
      <div>
        <strong>Components Used</strong>
        <p>Motors, sensors, materials, etc.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="check-item">
      <span class="check-icon">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12"/></svg>
      </span>
      <div>
        <strong>Performance Metrics</strong>
        <p>Speed, reliability, efficiency numbers</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="check-item">
      <span class="check-icon">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M14.7 6.3a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.4l1.6 1.6a1 1 0 0 0 1.4 0l3.77-3.77a6 6 0 0 1-7.94 7.94l-6.91 6.91a2.12 2.12 0 0 1-3-3l6.91-6.91a6 6 0 0 1 7.94-7.94l-3.76 3.76z"/></svg>
      </span>
      <div>
        <strong>Challenges &amp; Solutions</strong>
        <p>Problems encountered and how you fixed them</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2>Allocation Guidelines</h2>
  <p>
    Typically, Robot Subsystems take up <strong>3-5 pages</strong> of your portfolio. How many pages you give each one depends on:
  </p>

  <div class="alloc-factors">
    <div class="factor">
      <span class="factor-bar" style="width: 90%;"></span>
      <span class="factor-label">Complexity of each subsystem</span>
    </div>
    <div class="factor">
      <span class="factor-bar" style="width: 80%;"></span>
      <span class="factor-label">How much it evolved during the season</span>
    </div>
    <div class="factor">
      <span class="factor-bar" style="width: 70%;"></span>
      <span class="factor-label">Importance to your team's strategy</span>
    </div>
    <div class="factor">
      <span class="factor-bar" style="width: 60%;"></span>
      <span class="factor-label">How unique or innovative your solution is</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Sample Subsystem Page Layout -->
  <h2>Sample Subsystem Page</h2>
  <p>Here's how to lay out a single subsystem's page - start with a big image of the current design, then show your iteration timeline below:</p>

  <div class="subsys-layout">
    <div class="subsys-page">
      <div class="subsys-page-header">Drivetrain</div>
      <div class="subsys-page-body">
        <!-- Large current-design hero image -->
        <div class="subsys-hero-img">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="30" height="30" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" class="subsys-hero-icon"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/><path d="M19.4 15a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 .33 1.82l.06.06a2 2 0 0 1-2.83 2.83l-.06-.06A1.65 1.65 0 0 0 15 19.4a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1 1.51V21a2 2 0 0 1-4 0v-.09A1.65 1.65 0 0 0 9 19.4a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.82.33l-.06.06a2 2 0 0 1-2.83-2.83l.06-.06A1.65 1.65 0 0 0 4.68 15a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.51-1H3a2 2 0 0 1 0-4h.09A1.65 1.65 0 0 0 4.6 9a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-.33-1.82l-.06-.06a2 2 0 0 1 2.83-2.83l.06.06A1.65 1.65 0 0 0 9 4.68a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1-1.51V3a2 2 0 0 1 4 0v.09a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1 1.51 1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1.82-.33l.06-.06a2 2 0 0 1 2.83 2.83l-.06.06A1.65 1.65 0 0 0 19.4 9a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1.51 1H21a2 2 0 0 1 0 4h-.09a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.51 1z"/></svg>
          <span>Current Design - Photo / CAD Render</span>
        </div>

        <!-- Purpose -->
        <div class="subsys-desc-row">
          <div class="subsys-label">Purpose &amp; Design</div>
          <div class="subsys-line"></div>
          <div class="subsys-line short"></div>
        </div>

        <!-- Iteration Timeline -->
        <div class="subsys-label">Design Iterations</div>
        <div class="subsys-timeline">
          <div class="subsys-tl-item">
            <div class="subsys-tl-dot"></div>
            <div class="subsys-tl-card">
              <div class="subsys-tl-img">
                <span>v1</span>
              </div>
              <span class="subsys-tl-date">Sep</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="subsys-tl-item">
            <div class="subsys-tl-dot"></div>
            <div class="subsys-tl-card">
              <div class="subsys-tl-img">
                <span>v2</span>
              </div>
              <span class="subsys-tl-date">Nov</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="subsys-tl-item current">
            <div class="subsys-tl-dot accent"></div>
            <div class="subsys-tl-card">
              <div class="subsys-tl-img accent">
                <span>v3</span>
              </div>
              <span class="subsys-tl-date accent">Jan</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Specs -->
        <div class="subsys-specs-section">
          <div class="subsys-label">Specs</div>
          <div class="subsys-spec-row"><span>Motors</span><span>4× GoBilda</span></div>
          <div class="subsys-spec-row"><span>Speed</span><span>1.8 m/s</span></div>
          <div class="subsys-spec-row"><span>Weight</span><span>3.2 kg</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="subsys-notes">
      <div class="subsys-note">
        <span class="subsys-dot"></span>
        Large hero image of the <strong>current design</strong> dominates the top
      </div>
      <div class="subsys-note">
        <span class="subsys-dot"></span>
        Brief text explains purpose and key design choices
      </div>
      <div class="subsys-note">
        <span class="subsys-dot"></span>
        Timeline shows each iteration with thumbnails and dates
      </div>
      <div class="subsys-note">
        <span class="subsys-dot"></span>
        Specs table gives judges concrete, quantifiable numbers
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="callout tip">
    <strong><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: -0.15em; margin-right: 0.25em;"><path d="M15 14c.2-1 .7-1.7 1.5-2.5 1-.9 1.5-2.2 1.5-3.5A6 6 0 0 0 6 8c0 1 .2 2.2 1.5 3.5.7.7 1.3 1.5 1.5 2.5"></path><path d="M9 18h6"></path><path d="M10 22h4"></path></svg>Pro Tip:</strong> Use CAD renderings and photos to show your subsystems from different angles.
    Make sure each image has a clear caption explaining what judges are looking at.
  </div>

  <LessonNav 
    prev={{ title: "CAD & Technical Drawings", href: "/lessons/lesson-5/" }}
    next={{ title: "Software & Programming", href: "/lessons/lesson-7/" }}
  />
</Layout>

<style>
  .subsystem-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(180px, 1fr));
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin: 1.25rem 0 1.5rem;
  }

  .sub-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    padding: 1.15rem;
    background: var(--bg-surface-solid);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    transition: border-color 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
  }

  .sub-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--border-accent);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .sub-icon {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 42px;
    height: 42px;
    border-radius: 11px;
    background: var(--accent-faint);
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .sub-card strong {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-heading);
  }

  .sub-card p {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.45;
  }

  .doc-checklist {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(240px, 1fr));
    gap: 0.6rem;
    margin: 1rem 0 1.5rem;
  }

  .check-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    padding: 0.8rem 1rem;
    background: var(--bg-surface-hover);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    transition: background 0.15s ease;
  }

  .check-item:hover {
    background: var(--accent-faint);
  }

  .check-icon {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 28px;
    height: 28px;
    border-radius: 7px;
    background: var(--accent-faint);
    color: var(--accent);
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 1px;
  }

  .check-item strong {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    color: var(--text-heading);
    margin-bottom: 0.1rem;
  }

  .check-item p {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .alloc-factors {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin: 1.25rem 0 1.5rem;
    padding: 1.25rem;
    background: var(--bg-surface-solid);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  }

  .factor {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.35rem;
  }

  .factor-bar {
    display: block;
    height: 8px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-subtle));
    border-radius: 4px;
    transition: width 0.6s ease;
  }

  .factor-label {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  /* Subsystem page layout example */
  .subsys-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 260px 1fr;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    align-items: start;
    margin: 1.25rem 0 1.5rem;
  }

  .subsys-page {
    background: var(--bg-surface-solid);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    overflow: hidden;
    aspect-ratio: 8.5 / 11;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .subsys-page-header {
    background: var(--accent);
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    padding: 0.3rem 0.75rem;
    text-align: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .subsys-page-body {
    padding: 0.45rem 0.55rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.35rem;
    flex: 1;
    min-height: 0;
  }

  /* Large hero image for current design */
  .subsys-hero-img {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 0.25rem;
    width: 100%;
    flex: 1 1 0;
    min-height: 60px;
    max-height: 90px;
    background: var(--accent-faint);
    border: 1.5px dashed var(--border-accent);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
  }

  .subsys-hero-icon {
    color: var(--accent);
    opacity: 0.45;
  }

  .subsys-hero-img span {
    font-size: 0.45rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--accent);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 0 0.4rem;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .subsys-desc-row {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.15rem;
  }

  .subsys-label {
    font-size: 0.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--accent);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    margin-bottom: 0.05rem;
  }

  .subsys-line {
    height: 3px;
    background: var(--bg-surface-hover);
    border-radius: 3px;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .subsys-line.short {
    width: 80%;
  }

  /* Iteration Timeline */
  .subsys-timeline {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 0.25rem;
    position: relative;
    padding-top: 0;
  }

  /* Horizontal connecting line behind dots */
  .subsys-timeline::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 4px;
    left: 14px;
    right: 14px;
    height: 2px;
    background: var(--border);
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .subsys-tl-item {
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    gap: 0.2rem;
  }

  .subsys-tl-dot {
    width: 10px;
    height: 10px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--bg-surface-solid);
    border: 2px solid var(--border);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .subsys-tl-dot.accent {
    background: var(--accent);
    border-color: var(--accent);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px var(--accent-faint);
  }

  .subsys-tl-card {
    width: 100%;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.1rem;
    padding: 0 0.1rem;
  }

  .subsys-tl-img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 28px;
    background: var(--bg-surface-hover);
    border-radius: 3px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 0.48rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-weight: 700;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .subsys-tl-img.accent {
    background: var(--accent-faint);
    color: var(--accent);
    border-color: var(--accent);
  }

  .subsys-tl-date {
    font-size: 0.42rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .subsys-tl-date.accent {
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .subsys-specs-section {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.15rem;
    margin-top: auto;
  }

  .subsys-spec-row {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    font-size: 0.48rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    padding: 0.1rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px dotted var(--border);
  }

  .subsys-spec-row:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .subsys-notes {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.65rem;
    padding-top: 0.25rem;
  }

  .subsys-note {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .subsys-note strong {
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .subsys-dot {
    width: 8px;
    height: 8px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--accent);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .subsys-layout {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    .subsys-page {
      aspect-ratio: auto;
      max-width: 280px;
    }
    .subsys-hero-img {
      min-height: 80px;
      max-height: 100px;
    }
  }
</style>


